# StatusGator Provider

The StatusGator provider allows you to manage [StatusGator](https://statusgator.com) resources using Terraform. StatusGator is a status page aggregator that helps you monitor the status of third-party services and create your own status pages.

## Features

- **Monitor Groups**: Organize monitors into logical groups
- **Website Monitors**: Monitor HTTP endpoints with customizable checks
- **Ping Monitors**: Monitor servers via ICMP ping
- **Custom Monitors**: Create monitors with manually-controlled status
- **Service Monitors**: Track external status pages (AWS, GitHub, etc.)
- **Subscribers**: Manage email subscribers for status updates
- **Incidents**: Create and manage incidents and maintenance windows

